{"tid":1362572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［可以著草啦］元朗襲擊案七人48小時後獲保釋","createTime":"2019-07-25T02:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T02:24:08.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99939ba590542331673364bec95bc2e25622bc08","tid":1362572,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:02:56.000Z","msg":"警方繼續調查元朗星期日晚發生的暴力襲擊事件，警方凌晨在元朗拘捕1名32歲男子，令被捕人數增至12人，年齡介乎24至54歲，涉嫌非法集結，他們分別在屯門、元朗和機場被捕，其中7人獲准保釋候查，八月下旬向警方報到，其餘5人仍被扣留調查。警方指，部分被捕人士有黑社會背景，行動中檢獲多條藤條、木棍及木條。<br />\n<br />\n襲擊共造成45人受傷送院，目前仍有5人在屯門醫院留醫，當中1名男子危殆，1人嚴重，3人穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS . 畫家係第二日就提堂仲要無保釋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1143432&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1143432%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=65cebfa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1143432&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"37cbd8797409af898ed3a40da880563979e3b38a","tid":1362572,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:17:11.000Z","msg":"高調拉人 低調放人"},{"pid":"b59f6299af9d77eaf873c1bc6f51e2b367507ea3","tid":1362572,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K4DG9Hr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4DG9Hr.png&h=32ade980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n727 發動全港紀律部隊保護市民遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360600</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5263ed3b36875f47e647dca674155329f88072c7","tid":1362572,"uid":265707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:24:08.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n[置頂] 打完飛機未，打完就入黎傾正經野呀！！ 727 反黑遊行 5+1 訴求<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dpKaqS\" data-aut